@NODE "main" "iff2aiff - IFF to AIFF Converter"
Convert IFF audio to AIFF or AIFC format

iff2aiff is a command-line tool that converts IFF (Interchange File Format) sound files to Apple AIFF (Audio IFF) or AIFC with uncompressed PCM. It uses IFFSound.lib and follows the iffparse.library pattern.

@{"Overview" LINK "overview"}
